com.example.metrics.statistics

Interface Sequence<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<T>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    TotalizingSequence<T>

    public interface Sequence<T>
extends java.lang.Iterable<T>
    Interface with methods that add the behaviour of an ordered sequence, with pointers to its head and tails. It also keeps track of the size of the collection plus the ability to get elements randomly
